Utterance.UttText: In room 8 is Barbara abbott, 92 years old under Dr Vasquez, She is a new admission.
She came in with low blood pressure and the doctors have been questioning that maybe she have double dose her antihypertensives as she lives alone.
She might need a pharmacist referral and social worker referral for discharge planning.
She hasn't been seen by the team yet.
She is stable and the daughter is in attendance.
